                            <note>The spaces intended for the rubrics have been left blank on <locus from="5r" to="56r"/>.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ንጽሐፍ፡ እንከ፡ ነገረ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ዘተናገርዎ፡ ለቃውንት፡ ፫፻፲ወ፰ርቱዓነ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ 
